data.description: You will be glad you looked at this ''like new'' home in Cross Creek, featuring 4 bedrooms,, 21/2 baths and a bonus room.  Of special interest to Veterans is a low interest, fixed rate, assumable mortgage, available to a qualified buyer.. The seller will offer interest rate buy down . (See Documents) Zoned for Clay County's top-rated schools, Cross Creek is also conveniently located minutes away from all of Fleming Island's shopping and services. Plus, NAS JAX is a quick 25 minute drive away.  The amenity center features a clubhouse, pool, fitness center and sports courts.  Make this house yours  and enjoy all the comforts of ''Home'' at a great price.
